Company Overview
AT Investment Advisers, Inc. primarily provides its services to individuals, including high net worth individuals, investment companies, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, and state or municipal government entities. It manages separate client-focused portfolios. The firm also manages mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. The firm was formerly known as Stein Roe Investment Counsel, Inc. It operates as a subsidiary of Atlantic Trust Advisors, Inc. AT Investment Advisers, Inc. was founded in 1932 and is based in Chicago, Illinois with additional offices in New York, New York; San Franci...
AT Investment Advisers, Inc. primarily provides its services to individuals, including high net worth individuals, investment companies, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, and state or municipal government entities. It manages separate client-focused portfolios. The firm also manages mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. The firm was formerly known as Stein Roe Investment Counsel, Inc. It operates as a subsidiary of Atlantic Trust Advisors, Inc. AT Investment Advisers, Inc. was founded in 1932 and is based in Chicago, Illinois with additional offices in New York, New York; San Francisco, California; and Newport Beach, California. AT Investment Advisers, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Atlantic Trust Group, LLC.
